- User REST API:
POST /api/users/register                       # Register new User
POST /api/users/login                          # Login
POST /api/users/{id}/addresses/new             # Add new Address to User by ID
GET  /api/users/{id}                           # Get User by ID

- MenuCategory REST API:
POST /api/menu/categories                      # Create new Category
POST /api/menu/categories/{id}/transfer        # Transfer all products from one category to another
GET  /api/menu/categories                      # Get all Categories
GET  /api/menu/categories/{id}                 # Get Category by ID
GET  /api/menu/categories/{id}/products        # Get all Products by Category ID
DEL  /api/menu/categories/{id}                 # Delete Category by ID
PUT  /api/menu/categories/{id}                 # Update Category by ID

- MenuProduct REST API:
POST /api/menu/products                      # Create new Product
GET  /api/menu/products                      # Get all Products
GET  /api/menu/products/{id}                 # Get Product by ID
DEL  /api/menu/products/{id}                 # Delete Product by ID
PUT  /api/menu/products/{id}                 # Update Product by ID